 <fr:p>Without loss of generality, we may assume that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> has an <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-000W.xml"
title="Inverse"
addr="//erct/erct-000W"
type="local">inverse</fr:link> 
 <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen g,\epsilon ,\eta ,\chi \right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
. By <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-0026.xml"
title="Propositions are closed under retracts"
addr="//erct/erct-0026"
type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number
addr="//erct/erct-0026" /></fr:link>, it suffices to argue that the type of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="//erct/erct-001I"
type="local">inverses</fr:link> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-0025.xml"
title="Retract"
addr="//erct/erct-0025"
type="local">retract</fr:link> of a <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="//erct/erct-001I"
type="local">proposition</fr:link>; the type of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="//erct/erct-001I"
type="local">inverses</fr:link> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is in fact equivalent to the type of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-000Y.xml"
title="Section-retraction pair"
addr="//erct/erct-000Y"
type="local">sections</fr:link> equipped with a <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-0041.xml"
title="The coherent remainder of a section"
addr="//erct/erct-0041"
type="local">coherent remainder</fr:link>:</fr:p>
 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
  \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \sigma :\mathsf {section}\,f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \sigma :\mathsf {section}\,f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \sigma :\mathsf {section}\,f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \sigma :\mathsf {section}\,f\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}
  \mathsf {coherentRemainder}_{f}\sigma 
 ]]></fr:tex>

 <fr:p>By <fr:link
