  <fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B \colon  A \to  \mathsf {Type}]]></fr:tex> be a family of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="//erct/erct-001I"
type="local">propositions</fr:link>; fixing <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex>, it suffices to show any other <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g :\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx]]></fr:tex> may be identified with <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>. As <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is a family of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="//erct/erct-001I"
type="local">propositions</fr:link>, we know that each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml"
title="Contractible type"
addr="//erct/erct-001H"
type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[fx]]></fr:tex>. Therefore, the closure of <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml"
title="Contractible type"
addr="//erct/erct-001H"
type="local">contractible</fr:link> types under dependent products (<fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001A.xml"
title="Dependent product of contractible types"
addr="//erct/erct-001A"
type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number
addr="//erct/erct-001A" /></fr:link>) shows that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml"
title="Contractible type"
addr="//erct/erct-001H"
type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
